  isConversation: 1
  speakerName:
  - Pele
  - You
  - Pele
  - You
  - You
  - Pele
  - You
  - Pele
  - You
  - Pele
  paragraphs:
  - Traveler!
  - Jesus! Can you seriously stop doing that?
  - Now, tell me...what have you learned from this endeavor?
  - This land is sacred...it is sacred and it must be respected at all times, for
    it has been here longer than I.
  - We should not take what is not meant for us.
  - Good...and what else?
  - The forest remembers all transgressions...the powers of this land are not to
    be misjudged.
  - Well said. Let this be a lesson.
  - How do I leave this forest?
  - Like this.
